features: 【High Carbon German Stainless Steel Laser-engraved Pattern(Not Damascus Pattern )】 MOSFiATA 8 inch pro chef's knife is made of premier high carbon German EN1.4116 stainless steel with high strength and increased rigidity. The kitchen knife contains 0.45-0.55% carbon, twice hardness than other knives, which will maintain longer sturdiness function.Laser-engraved pattern on the blade surface for decoration & anti-sticking.(NOTE: Different from Damascus pattern! Don't be confused!)

【Razor Sharp Edge & Anti-Corrosion, Anti-Tarnish Blade】Processed with the unique polishing technology and hand sharpened 16°per side, the chef kitchen knife's blade tapers from the spine to the cutting edge, for effortless precision cutting, as well as greater stability and durability. 15% chrome which provides corrosion resistance and an anti-tarnish finish.

【Full Tang Construction & Ergonomic Design】 MOSFiATA ergonomic knife handle is made of santoprene for comfort and polypropylene for durability. It features textured finger points that provide slip resistance and a better grip. The solid Micarta handle can minimize wrist tension while providing a secure, comfortable grip no matter the size of your hand or where you are gripping the handle. Triple riveted Micarta handle to the precise forged full tang for extra strength & durability.

【Professional Kitchen Chef Knife】The multifunctional cooking knife can easily handle your daily kitchen tasks of cutting, slicing, chopping, mincing and dicing of fruits, vegetables and all kind of meat. A professional and all-rounder home cooks knife for you.

【Exquisite Gift Box】- Our kitchen knife set packed in a stylish black presentation box, comes with a stainless steel finger guard, a knife sharpener and a blade guard. Thoughtful design and an excellent gift idea for friends, family, and special occasions such as birthdays, weddings, anniversaries, and more.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why Choose The MOSFiATA 8-inch Chef Knife? MOSFiATA knives are made of high-quality German stainless steel, which resists rust, corrosion, and discoloration. The razor-sharp edge is easy to maintain and makes cutting and chopping a breeze. Inside the Gift Box, you get not only a professional chef knife, but also a finger protector, blade guard and knife sharpener. It will help you with all your kitchen tasks and alleviate all your concerns. 1: Rust-resistant, 2.5mm stainless steel blade 2: Nonstick blade coating that keeps food from sticking to the knife while cutting 3: Sturdy, TPR-coated polypropylene handle with for comfortable cutting 4: Ultra sharp, curved edge for easy slicing, mincing & dicing 5: Multi-functional design for cutting anything & everything in the kitchen, from meat to tough vegetables 6: Top-rack dishwasher safe – no rust, stains or corrosion

ALL-AROUND CHEF KNIFE This professional chef knife can easily handle your daily kitchen tasks of slicing, dicing and mincing by cutting fruit, vegetables and meat. Comfortable Handle The handle is made from Santoprene for comfort and polypropylene for durability. It features textured finger points that provide slip resistance and a better grip. Each handle is engineered to gently widen where it meets the blade to help protect fingers. Ultra-Sharp The precision-forged blade ensures reliable performance, with every cut sure to impress. It has a longer edge than an ordinary knife, and it is resilient due to the extreme hardness of HRC 56+ Made of German steel 4116, this durable blade is built to last a long time. The superb alloy prevents dulling and rust, and it maintains the original sharpness over time.

Micarta Handles Non-slip Micarta handle with a lightweight and comfortable grip that makes long hours in the kitchen easy. Strong and Durable The 8-inch kitchen knife made from high-quality stainless steel can be used for hard tasks and still maintain its functionality for a very long time. Ultra Sharp Edge Sharpness is key to achieving the best cuts. The knife's blade is quite sharp and will remain that way even after tough tasks such as cutting bones or greasy meat. Knife Sharpener Included With knife sharpener and finger protector included, you have all you need for successful food preparation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very sharp and cuts well. I prefer knives a little heavier but it feels good and gets the job done.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This knife was very impressive. It is super sharp. I like that it came with a blade cover to protect it, and also had a knife sharpener with it. It cuts everything with ease. Great valve for the money. I recommend it to everyone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A really nice chefs knife
reviews.reviewText: Even the wife said this was a beautiful knife. The knife come fairly sharp but has been sharpened with anabrasive belt which leaves a rough edge. I ran it thru the included ceramic sharpener, a few strokes, which smoothed the edge and made it sharper. How it holds that edge remains to be seen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good value and sharp enough
reviews.reviewText: This is sharp enough for us, and cuts better than other knives except the top end knives that are dangerously sharp and expensive. comes with a sharpener and guard.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My boyfriend loves it
reviews.reviewText: My boyfriend isn’t a top tier chef, but he does really love to cook. He was complaining about the knives he was using for a while and so I bought him a new one. He loves it! It’s super sharp, has amazing weight distribution, has a very pretty design, and cuts amazingly. Warning: Do not use the hand sharpener! Those sharpeners will mess up your knife if used incorrectly (it is very easy to use a knife sharpener incorrectly), this one included. My boyfriend and I knew that’s before buying, so that didn’t matter to us. Get a normal knife sharpener and use that. Made a great gift! He uses it all the time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My wife is a grill cook and absolutely loves it. Won't let any of her co-workers use it. Very sharp,good weight and keep a sharp edge

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The Best Knife I have ever held in my hands
reviews.reviewText: I have never owned a knife as good as this and I also own a set of Zwilling knives. I am not complaining about the Zwelling's, they are great, but I must tell you these MOSFiATA knives are simply awesome! Balance, Fit to my grip, they are so sharp I can slice a tomato so thin I can see through it!!! I cannot say enough about these knives! I am planning to buy a set for my Chef son who loves them too!!I'm not a Chef but I love to cook and my oldest son is a Chef so we have a lot of conversations about the culinary world!!
